Ini demi kebaikan awak.

89
00:04:19,399 --> 00:04:21,399
Wang Sheng, saya memang berasa cara kamu

90
00:04:21,520 --> 00:04:22,080
sudah salah!

91
00:04:23,480 --> 00:04:26,000
Jadi, adakah awak akan mengambil ujian?

92
00:04:26,559 --> 00:04:27,200
Saya akan menerima cabaran

93
00:04:27,720 --> 00:04:28,399
di arena.

94
00:04:33,079 --> 00:04:33,640
Bagus.

95
00:04:37,079 --> 00:04:37,959
Apa yang akan berlaku
sekiranya saya tak pergi?

96
00:04:40,839 --> 00:04:41,480
Tahukah awak?

97
00:04:42,799 --> 00:04:43,320
Hal awak

98
00:04:44,040 --> 00:04:45,799
dipesan khas oleh Tuan Ye Zhiqiu.

99
00:04:47,239 --> 00:04:48,040
Ketua pasukan sangat mementingkan juga.

100
00:04:49,679 --> 00:04:51,920
Jika awak tidak mahu menerima cabaran,

101
00:04:52,239 --> 00:04:54,279
