135
00:06:30,079 --> 00:06:30,720
Adakah awak nak pergi?

136
00:06:31,440 --> 00:06:32,079
Saya akan tinggal di sini.

137
00:06:32,559 --> 00:06:33,640
Mengapa?

138
00:06:35,480 --> 00:06:36,760
Ada satu hal yang sangat penting,

139
00:06:37,519 --> 00:06:38,959
