141
00:06:41,480 --> 00:06:42,079
Abang San.

142
00:06:42,160 --> 00:06:42,559
Ya.

143
00:06:42,600 --> 00:06:43,959
Kita Tujuh Raksasa Shi Lanke, bukan?

144
00:06:44,559 --> 00:06:45,760
Kami ada di sini
jika ada apa yang berlaku,

145
00:06:45,839 --> 00:06:46,480
kita boleh menghadapi bersama.

146
00:06:46,720 --> 00:06:47,279
Ya.

147
00:06:47,399 --> 00:06:48,239
Kami boleh membantu.

148
00:06:48,239 --> 00:06:48,920
Terima kasih.

149
00:06:49,559 --> 00:06:51,920
Tapi, saya ingin
menyelesaikan hal itu sendiri,

150
00:06:52,320 --> 00:06:53,279
