untuk selamanya, cikgu.

179
00:08:02,440 --> 00:08:03,519
Apakah maksud awak?

180
00:08:03,880 --> 00:08:04,959
Sudah tentu awak murid saya.

181
00:08:05,440 --> 00:08:06,880
Saya takkan membiarkan awak di sini.

182
00:08:07,480 --> 00:08:07,920
Cikgu...

183
00:08:07,959 --> 00:08:09,239
Sudah, itu sahaja.

184
00:08:10,200 --> 00:08:11,079
Bersama-sama kita...

185
00:08:13,440 --> 00:08:14,440
Menghantar mereka.

186
00:08:30,040 --> 00:08:30,760
Cikgu.

187
00:08:31,519 --> 00:08:33,079
Betulkah awak
nak membiarkan Abang San di sini?

188
00:08:35,239 --> 00:08:36,440
Satu hari nanti,

189
00:08:36,519 --> 00:08:37,760
kamu pasti akan meninggalkan Shi Lanke.

190
00:08:38,320 --> 00:08:39,520
Apakah awak berharap

191
00:08:39,880 --> 00:08:41,239
kamu ditahan di situ selama-lamanya?

192
00:08:43,919 --> 00:08:44,919
Tapi, awak dikecualikan.

193
00:08:45,239 --> 00:08:47,000
Awak perlu melangsaikan hutang yuran

194
00:08:47,000 --> 00:08:47,719
sebelum menamatkan pelajaran.

195
00:08:48,119 --> 00:08:48,640
Saya...

196
00:08:49,440 --> 00:08:51,200
Saya sudah menjadi anak murid cikgu.

197
00:08:52,200 --> 00:08:54,200
Saya boleh pertimbangkan
untuk merendahkan kadar bunga.

198
00:09:00,799 --> 00:09:01,479
Abang Dai.

199
00:09:01,840 --> 00:09:03,239
Mengapa Tang San
tak nak pergi dari sini?

200
00:09:05,479 --> 00:09:06,239
Dia pasti ada alasan tertentu

201
00:09:07,000 --> 00:09:08,080
jika tidak memberitahu kita.

202
00:09:08,919 --> 00:09:10,400
Semua orang mempunyai rahsia,

203
00:09:11,159 --> 00:09:12,119
kita tak semestinya tahu.

204
00:09:13,239 --> 00:09:14,039
Percaya pada dia saja.

205
00:09:17,359 --> 00:09:18,559
Betulkah awak
tak memerlukan pertolongan kami?

206
00:09:19,640 --> 00:09:21,359
Ya, saya boleh menyelesaikan sendiri.

207
00:09:26,080 --> 00:09:26,760
Sudah.

208
00:09:27,320 --> 00:09:28,359
Pintu keluar kota ada di depan,

209
00:09:29,039 --> 00:09:29,960
hantar sampai sini saja.

210
00:09:42,239 --> 00:09:44,760
Sudah, baik kamu bergegas.

211
00:09:45,119 --> 00:09:46,320
Mana tahu kita dapat berjumpa lagi

212
00:09:47,080 --> 00:09:48,039
di Kota Tiandou?

213
00:09:52,119 --> 00:09:52,679
Tang San.

214
00:09:55,640 --> 00:09:57,320
Cari saya jika awak menghadapi masalah,

215
00:09:58,840 --> 00:10:00,400
saya pengetua awak selamanya.

216
00:10:06,000 --> 00:10:06,599
Abang San.

217
00:10:09,440 --> 00:10:10,840
Apa hal? Mengapa menangis?

218
00:10:10,919 --> 00:10:11,919
Ingat kata-kata saya,

219
00:10:13,239 --> 00:10:15,679
