pada bila-bila masa.

220
00:10:19,599 --> 00:10:20,599
Jaga diri, kawan.

221
00:10:30,119 --> 00:10:30,679
Sudah.

222
00:10:33,640 --> 00:10:34,760
Apa yang kamu buat?

223
00:10:36,280 --> 00:10:38,679
Mengapa tak beritahu lebih awal?

224
00:10:39,159 --> 00:10:41,239
Tiba-tiba saja kata nak berpisah,

225
00:10:42,400 --> 00:10:44,000
