226
00:10:50,280 --> 00:10:51,840
Kita akan berjumpa lagi.

227
00:10:52,200 --> 00:10:54,520
Xiao Wu, beritahu kami

228
00:10:55,159 --> 00:10:56,039
apabila kamu memerlukan bantuan.

229
00:10:58,559 --> 00:10:59,479
Sudahlah.

230
00:10:59,479 --> 00:11:00,479
Jangan menangis lagi.

231
00:11:01,559 --> 00:11:02,919
Setiap pertemuan pasti ada perpisahan,

232
00:11:02,919 --> 00:11:04,520
pasti ada pertemuan semula
selepas perpisahan.

233
00:11:05,080 --> 00:11:07,039
Kamu akan meninggalkan
Shi Lanke satu hari nanti,

234
00:11:07,719 --> 00:11:09,719
dunia yang lebih menarik
sedang menunggu.

235
00:11:10,719 --> 00:11:11,320
Jangan menangis lagi.

236
00:11:12,640 --> 00:11:13,200
Mari bertolak.

237
00:11:18,960 --> 00:11:19,599
